snippet.title: VENGE.IO - 19 KILLSTREAK - EPIC GAMEPLAY
snippet.description:
#venge #vengeio
Venge.io is an online multiplayer shooter where you will face two other real players on a battlefield.

Your mission will be simple, you must find the green areas of the map and claim that area before your opponents do. When capturing the area you will receive special ability cards that you can use, pressing the B key, to improve your equipment and make you stronger.

You can change weapons when you reappear in the game so no round will be boring. There are several weapons to choose from, such as Scar, Shotgun, Tec-9 and even a sniper rifle, where you can hide in a good place and end up with a headshot with all your enemies.

Right now in Venge.io you only have one character named Lilium, who for sure will be able to choose others very soon in the next update of the game.

You can invite two friends by sharing a link on the lobby screen and enjoy this incredible game together!

Who created Venge.io?
It was developed by Cem Demir, the creator behind Robofight and MiniRoyale2.io

Game: Venge
